name: Lucille Tenazas
biography:
Born in Aklan, Philippines on 17 December 1953.
Education: College of Holy Spiritm Manila B.F.A. in 1975, Cranbrook Academy of Art M.F.A. in 1981.  
Established Tenazas Design in San Francisco in 1985 and aalso became adjunct professor at California College of Arts.
